  "title": "Plant Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Jurong Island<br /></p><p>Site Allowance + travel allowance provided<br /></p><p>Manage</p><ul><li>Operation and maintenance of Wastewater treatment plant (WWTP)</li><li>Daily performance log management of WWTP Plant;</li><li>Daily monitoring of plant performance;</li><li>Preventive maintenance of mechanical equipment;</li><li>Preventive maintenance of electrical and Instruments;</li><li>Electrical & Instruments Component Health check;</li><li>Daily chemical top up and maintain the correct level;</li><li>Daily reporting to management of plant performance;</li><li>Calibration of Instruments as per schedule;</li><li>Ensure WWTP compliance with ISO standards;</li><li>Control and Monitoring system review;</li><li>Conduct daily housekeeping and 5s;</li><li>Coordination of groundstaffs;</li><li>Manpower planning;</li><li>Management of sludge dewatering unit;</li><li>Management of Chemical dosing units;</li><li>Conduct minor maintenance (bi-monthly) and major maintenance (bi-annually)</li></ul>",
